      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "rationale": "Boundary conditions in the simulation are matched to experimental conditions using a systematic parameter mapping: inlet flow rate matched to ±0.5% of experimental setpoint, rotational speed matched to ±5 RPM, fluid viscosity matched to measured value at test temperature. Residual mismatches between simulation inputs and experimental conditions are quantified and propagated through the uncertainty budget. All five operating points demonstrate equivalent input parameter specification at Gradation 4.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
