        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Input parameter equivalency acceptance criteria",
        "description": "Simulation boundary conditions must be traceable to experimental measurements with documented tolerances. Residual mismatches must be quantified and included in the uncertainty budget. Parameter mapping must be documented for all primary inputs."
